<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CarHouse - Page Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <style>
        .error-page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #0a0a0a 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-content {
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .error-code span {
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        .error-message {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .error-description {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #fff;
            opacity: 0.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .error-actions .btn {
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .error-actions .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent-color);
            border: none;
        }

        .error-actions .btn-outline-light:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .error-background {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('/images/error-bg.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
            opacity: 0.1;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .error-particles {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .error-particles::before,
        .error-particles::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 2px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--accent-color);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: particle 3s infinite;
        }

        .error-particles::before {
            top: 20%;
            left: 20%;
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }

        .error-particles::after {
            top: 60%;
            left: 80%;
            animation-delay: 1.5s;
        }

        @keyframes particle {
            0% {
                transform: translate(0, 0);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translate(100px, 100px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .error-code {
                font-size: 6rem;
            }

            .error-message {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .error-description {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .error-actions {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .error-actions .btn {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-page">
        <div class="error-background"></div>
        <div class="error-particles"></div>
        <div class="error-content">
            <h1 class="error-code">4<span>0</span>4</h1>
            <p class="error-message">Page Not Found</p>
            <p class="error-description">
                The page you're looking for seems to have taken a detour. Let's get you back on track to finding your dream car.
            </p>
            <div class="error-actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Back to Home
                </a>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light">
                    <i class="fas fa-car me-2"></i>Explore Cars
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 